==Documentation==
This template creates a full platform page layout with hero section, tabs, wiki content, and sidebar.
Uses Semantic MediaWiki for structured data storage and display.

Platforms are gaming hardware systems - consoles, handhelds, computers, and other devices that run games.

===Parameters===
{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Parameter !! Description
|-
|| Name || Display name of the platform
|-
|| Guid || Giant Bomb API identifier
|-
|| Aliases || Alternative names (comma-separated)
|-
|| Image || Platform image filename
|-
|| BackgroundImage || Background image filename
|-
|| Deck || Short description shown in hero
|-
|| ShortName || Abbreviation (e.g., PS5, XSX, NSW)
|-
|| ReleaseDate || Platform release date
|-
|| InstallBase || Number of units sold
|-
|| OnlineSupport || Online service name (e.g., PlayStation Network)
|-
|| OriginalPrice || Launch price
|-
|| Manufacturer || Company that made the platform (page link)
|}

